window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Cassio King.</p> <p>My savior.</p> <p>My enemy.</p> <p>The man lurked in the shadows of my dreams. He was supposed to marry my cousin.</p> <p>Yet, here I was...taking her place.</p> <p>I’ve hated the King family for as long as I could remember. Certain things were unforgivable. But there was more to Cassio than meets the eye.</p> <p>Could I find my happily ever after and avenge the harm his family had done to me and my father?</p> <p>Possible trigger warnings: This book contains some disturbing scenes related to abuse and human trafficking. If you are offended by such scenes, this book might not be for you.</p>"; 
